FuncDef: This command configures the type of a queue group redirect list. The default value isvxlan-vni, which is the only possible value.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the type of the queue group redirect list. The queue group redirect list is used to match VXLAN VNIs in IPv4 and IPv6 VXLAN or VXLAN GPE packets. Values-vxlan-vni.
